ZH: 他患有精神病，需要定期就医。
EN: He suffers from mental illness and needs regular medical treatment.

ZH: 精神病患者需要得到及时的心理支持。
EN: Patients with mental illness need timely psychological support.

ZH: 家庭成员应该帮助精神病患者获得正确的治疗。
EN: Family members should help mental illness patients get proper treatment.

ZH: 心理健康对预防精神病有重要作用。
EN: Mental health plays an important role in preventing mental illness.

ZH: 这种精神病需要特殊的药物治疗。
EN: This type of mental illness requires special medication treatment.

ZH: 精神病可能会影响患者的日常生活。
EN: Mental illness may affect the patient's daily life.

ZH: 患有精神病的人需要社区的支持和关怀。
EN: People with mental illness need support and care from the community.

ZH: 了解精神病的症状可以帮助及时诊断。
EN: Understanding the symptoms of mental illness can help with timely diagnosis.

ZH: 精神病并不意味着患者无法康复。
EN: Mental illness does not mean that patients cannot recover.

ZH: 精神病患者需要家人的理解和支持。
EN: Mental illness patients need understanding and support from their families.

ZH: 发展心理健康习惯有助于预防精神病。
EN: Developing healthy mental habits can help prevent mental illness.

ZH: 精神病可能需要长期治疗和康复计划。
EN: Mental illness may require long-term treatment and recovery plans.

ZH: 社会对精神病患者需要更多的关注和支持。
EN: Society needs to pay more attention and support to people with mental illness.

ZH: 精神病的症状有时会不明显，需要及时就医检查。
EN: The symptoms of mental illness are sometimes not obvious and require timely medical examination.

ZH: 心理治疗可以帮助患有精神病的人恢复。
EN: Psychotherapy can help people with mental illness recover.

ZH: 精神病患者需要生活中的积极支持和鼓励。
EN: Mental illness patients need positive support and encouragement in their lives.

ZH: 精神病治疗需要综合多方面的方法。
EN: The treatment of mental illness requires a comprehensive approach.

ZH: 精神病对患者的身心都会产生影响。
EN: Mental illness can affect both the physical and mental health of patients.

ZH: 精神病的发作可能会对患者的周围环境造成不利影响。
EN: The onset of mental illness may have a detrimental effect on the patient's surroundings.

ZH: 了解精神病可以帮助人们更好地理解患者的需要。
EN: Understanding mental illness can help people better understand the needs of patients.
